    local: { show: true, headline: 'Around Madison This Month', text: 'Bundle up and head to the <strong>Dane County Farmers\' Market Winter Market</strong> at the Monona Terrace (Saturdays through April). Also worth checking out: if you\'re into ice fishing, the lakes are frozen solid \u2014 grab a spot on Mendota or Monona before the February crowds.' },
