    review: { text: 'TotalGuard did an amazing spring cleanup on our property. They were thorough, on time, and left everything looking perfect. Already booked them for the full season.', name: 'Mauricio Roldan' },
    textBody: 'Hi {{first_name}},\n\nFebruary is planning season. Here\'s your spring prep checklist:\n\n1. Plan spring yard tasks now \u2014 walk your property and take stock.\n2. Test your soil pH \u2014 grab a test kit from UW-Extension for $20.\n3. Prep your tools \u2014 sharpen mower blades, change oil, clean the garage.\n\nSpring Cleanup Booking Is Open \u2014 Save 15%! Book before March 1.\n\n"TotalGuard did an amazing spring cleanup. Thorough, on time, and left everything looking perfect." \u2014 Mauricio Roldan\n\nBook at tgyardcare.com or call (608) 535-6057'
